 our next few tips and tutorials where we will explain more on how to<strong> Buy and Sell shares </strong>on TradeHero, as well as <strong>How to Earn Real Money</strong> using our application. Stay tuned!','Tutorial Part One: Introduction','','inherit','closed','open','','227-revision-23','','','2013-07-03 11:23:36','2013-07-03 03:23:36','',227,'http://blog.tradehero.mobi/227-revision-23',0,'revision','',0),(327,1,'2013-06-24 16:34:24','2013-06-24 08:34:24','','Home-Test','','inherit','closed','open','','320-revision-4','','','2013-06-24 16:34:24','2013-06-24 08:34:24','',320,'http://blog.tradehero.mobi/320-revision-4',0,'revision','',0),(328,1,'2013-06-24 16:43:58','2013-06-24 08:43:58','Slide 1 - Hello','Slide1','','publish','closed','closed','','slide1','','','2013-06-24 16:43:58','2013-06-24 08:43:58','',0,'http://blog.tradehero.mobi/?post_type=vp_orbitslides&#038;p=328',0,'vp_orbitslides','',0),(329,1,'2013-06-24 16:44:27','2013-06-24 08:44:27','','923031_10200877358632810_1616242512_n','Take a Position. Trade.','inherit','closed','open','','923031_10200877358632810_1616242512_n','','','2013-06-24 16:44:27','2013-06-24 08:44:27','',328,'http://blog.tradehero.mobi/wp-content/uploads/923031_10200877358632810_1616242512_n.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(330,1,'2013-06-24 16:42:48','2013-06-24 08:42:48','','Home-Test','','inherit','closed','open','','320-revision-5','','','2013-06-24 16:42:48','2013-06-24 08:42:48','',320,'http://blog.tradehero.mobi/320-revision-5',0,'revision','',0),(339,1,'2013-06-24 17:14:36','2013-06-24 09:14:36','','New Slider','','publish','closed','open','','new-slider','','','2013-10-22 17:43:54','2013-10-22 09:43:54','',0,'http://blog.tradehero.mobi/?post_type=ml-slider&#038;p=339',0,'ml-slider','',0),(331,1,'2013-06-24 16:45:09','2013-06-24 08:45:09','[orbit-slider]','Home-Test','','inherit','closed','open','','320-revision-6','','','2013-06-24 16:45:09','2013-06-24 08:45:09','',320,'http://blog.tradehero.mobi/320-revision-6',0,'re